emails.body:

Having trouble viewing this email?  View online https://t.update.nab.com.au/r/?id=t2f698461,76434a8,43c5399&p1=%40gGniUf37VoTVS4sqEJOtxEdTCjB4%2FYH7kmShG9oIEDQ%3D   

Your NAB Goodies have arrived.

Bernhard, get rewarded with your NAB Goodies offers – it’s our way of thanking you for banking with us. 
Your offers are all in the NAB app 

Featured offer:

Your exclusive internet offer is here.
Get MATE’s rates on your home internet. Save $300 on your internet bills in the first year, then $240 off each year after that (1).

More NAB Goodies



                
                
                $10 cashback when you spend $100 or more in one transaction at City Beach.

This offer is activated. Offer commences 06 October 2025. Redeem online by 09 November 2025.

T&Cs apply*            
                To redeem your offers, make a qualifying purchase using any of your eligible personal NAB cards. Cashback is limited to one per customer per offer and you'll usually receive your cashback within 14 business days (unless we tell you otherwise).  
 
                Get your NAB Goodies  
   
To find NAB Goodies, login to the NAB app and tap the Goodies tile on your Accounts screen.

Find out more at https://t.update.nab.com.au/r/?id=t2f698461,76434a8,43c539b&cid=edm:ac:117764569:124007592:23175319:81389767220b810801950de43579b134f13c05bc63f02a8f9e4aa4bac4d00a15&ac_cid=awsprodDM250355&ac_bid=23175319

                Download or update the NAB app

Download on the App Store at https://t.update.nab.com.au/r/?id=t2f698461,76434a8,43c539c

Get it on Google Play at https://t.update.nab.com.au/r/?id=t2f698461,76434a8,43c539d

                
                

                

                

                Good to know 

*Offer Terms and Conditions 

Offer 1:City Beach

Offer is eligible for online and in-store payments by a NAB personal Visa debit card, credit card or NAB Now Pay Later digital card. Offer is limited to 1 cashback(s) per customer. Offer cannot be used in conjunction with any other offer.
View Location: https://www.citybeach.com.au/find-stores

                                         Offer 2:Bras n Things
            
Offer is eligible for online payments only by a NAB personal Visa debit card, credit card or NAB Now Pay Later digital card. Offer is limited to 10 cashback(s) per customer. Excludes department stores, factory outlets, clearance stores and other authorised retailers. Only available direct with the partner providing the offer.
 
                                         Offer 3:Shoes and Sox
            
Offer is eligible for online and in-store payments by a NAB personal Visa debit card, credit card or NAB Now Pay Later digital card. Offer is limited to 10 cashback(s) per customer. Only available at participating locations in Australia (refer to store list).
View Location: https://shoesandsox.com.au/pages/store-locator
                                         Offer 4:Boody

This email address isn't monitored by our customer team. If you'd like to get in touch with us, please use one of the options contained on our website https://t.update.nab.com.au/r/?id=t2f698461,76434a8,43c539f&cid=edm:ac:117764569:124007592:23175319:81389767220b810801950de43579b134f13c05bc63f02a8f9e4aa4bac4d00a15&ac_cid=awsprodDM250355&ac_bid=23175319

(1) NABMATE Promotion:

Between 12:00am AEST on 1 September 2025 and 11:59pm AEST 31 August 2026, NAB customers who are new or existing Mate customers can receive a special promotion on their Eligible Product supplied by Mate:
•  $30 per month for the first six months; and 
•  $20 per month thereafter until the promotional discount comes to an end.

To be eligible for the special promotion, you’ll need to:
•   pay Mate with a personal Visa debit card issued by NAB, a personal Visa credit card issued by NAB, a NAB Now Pay Later (NNPL) digital card issued by NAB, a business Visa debit card issued by NAB or a business Visa credit card issued by NAB; and
•  choose a broadband plan offered by Mate, except the Ripper 50/20 or No Dramas Wireless.

To redeem this special promotion: 
•  new to Mate customers: head to the NAB x mate partnership page, apply for an eligible plan and apply the NABMATE promotional code during your application; or 
•  existing Mate customers: contact Mate by email, live chat or on the NAB goodies x mate hotline at 1300 182 829 and ask Mate to apply the NABMATE promotional code to your plan. 

The special promotion will stop being applied to your account if: 
•  you no longer pay your Mate bill with one of the NAB cards described above; or 
•  you breach Mate’s Customer Terms; or 
•  you move to a broadband plan which is not eligible for the discount; or
•  588 months pass from the date the promotional discount is first applied to your account
(whichever is earlier).

The special promotional discount may be varied or withdrawn at any time. Full terms and conditions are available at Mate’s website at https://t.update.nab.com.au/r/?id=t2f698461,76434a8,43c53a0

*General Terms on all Offers.

NAB Goodies "My Offers" offers (Offers) are available for selected NAB customers with eligible NAB cards only.

Offers cannot be transferred, exchanged, or redeemed for cash or other credits. To be eligible for Offers, transactions must be made with your personal NAB Visa debit, credit or NAB Now Pay Later digital card (eligible NAB card) within the specified Offer Period. 

Offers are only available to NAB customers who have an active, open and valid eligible NAB card with any linked account being open and not in default, opted in to access to offers in the Goodies section of the NAB app, and have met the eligibility criteria outlined in the NAB Goodies "My Offers" Terms and Conditions https://t.update.nab.com.au/r/?id=t2f698461,76434a8,43c53a1&cid=edm:ac:117764569:124007592:23175319:81389767220b810801950de43579b134f13c05bc63f02a8f9e4aa4bac4d00a15&ac_cid=awsprodDM250355&ac_bid=23175319 .

Offers do not apply if the transaction is made using another third-party establishment or payment processor to which your NAB Visa debit, credit or NAB Now Pay Later digital card is connected. This includes (but is not limited to) PayPal, AfterPay, Stripe, Shopify or BPAY®.

Unless specified otherwise, Cashbacks for Offers will be credited to your eligible NAB card (or its linked account if applicable) that was used to make the qualifying transaction within 14 business days of making a qualifying transaction (although sometimes it may take longer). 

You will become ineligible for the offers and not receive your cashback (even if you have made a qualifying transaction) if your eligible NAB card is inactive, cancelled or replaced (or where applicable its linked account is closed) or if you opt out of access to offers in the Goodies section of the NAB app at any time prior to NAB crediting your account. Acting reasonably, NAB has the right to withdraw or claim back any reward related to conduct it deems to have arisen out of fraud or wilful misconduct.

Cashback is limited one per customer per offer unless specified otherwise. NAB reserves the right to vary or end an Offer prior to its end date. If the change is unfavourable, we will try to publish details before the change takes effect, if we are reasonably able to do so. There may be instances which are outside our reasonable control where you are unable to redeem one or more of the Offers, e.g. a third party merchant withdraws or varies the terms of the Offer, a third party merchant is delayed in processing your purchase, a third party merchant uses a name or merchant category code which we cannot reasonably identify them as the relevant qualifying merchant under an offer. Except to the extent provided by law, we accept no liability if you are unable to redeem an offer or suffer a loss as a result of circumstances beyond our reasonable control.

🔥 SHRED HARD. TORCH FAT. KEEP GAINS.🔥

Introducing the Ultimate Shred Stack: S4 + MK-2866 + Cardarine

If you're serious about cutting fat without sacrificing
hard-earned muscle, it's time to fuel your body with
science-backed precision. Our elite SARMs Recomp Stack featuring
S4 (Andarine), MK-2866 (Ostarine), and Cardarine (GW-501516) is
designed to torch stubborn fat, preserve lean mass, and boost
endurance — all in one powerful cycle.

✅ S4 (Andarine) – The Sculptor
------------------------------

Shred fat with surgical precision. S4 targets androgen receptors
in muscle and bone to promote dry, vascular muscle gains while
aiding in fat oxidation. Expect enhanced muscle hardness and
definition that shows even at rest.

✅ MK-2866 (Ostarine) – The Protector
------------------------------------

Ostarine is your anabolic shield during a calorie deficit. It’s
clinically proven to preserve and even build lean muscle tissue
while cutting. Experience strength maintenance, recovery
acceleration, and that "full" muscle look — even in a cut.

✅ Cardarine (GW-501516) – The Engine
------------------------------------

Push beyond limits. Cardarine ramps up your metabolism and
increases endurance, allowing for longer, harder training
sessions. It promotes fat loss through enhanced fatty acid
utilization — meaning more energy, less fat, and zero muscle
loss.

⚙️ SYNERGY IN ACTION⚙️

----------------------

When combined, this trio forms the ultimate recomposition weapon
helping you shed fat, sculpt lean muscle, and elevate performance
in and out of the gym. Perfect for athletes, bodybuilders, or
anyone chasing a sharper, harder, more defined physique.

Results to Expect in 4–10 Weeks
✔ Noticeable fat loss
✔ Preserved or increased lean muscle
✔ Boosted strength & vascularity
✔ Improved stamina & recovery
✔ Dry, aesthetic definition

* S4 can cause light sensitivity-this will go away the day after

* It is always best to cycle any Sarms that require PCT with
Nizarol 1%-2% to prevent DHT build up on your scalp- This is
available at any chemist.

Eat in a calorie deficit

* Aim for about 500 Calories less than you need to maintain your
weight
* You need to be burning off more energy than you take in.
* Stick to lean, complete proteins like chicken, fish and lean
meats. For fats, choose healthy sources like oils and avocados,
with a small amount of saturated fats from meat and dairy.

Slight changes to your workout routine

A lot of people make the mistake of changing their training too
much when going on a cut. Traditionally, most muscle is gained in
the 8 to 12 rep range.

What you don’t want to do when starting a cut is to suddenly drop
the weights and only use a high rep routine. This is a recipe to
lose hard-earned muscle gained from your bulk. What you want to
do is train with the heaviest weight you can within the 8-12 rep
range and stick to what helped you put on muscle in the first
place.

Your weightlifting workouts should be used to help keep your
muscle mass as high as possible, not to lose body fat. This
